front.title: •Wokling (V)
front.gametext: Unless Massassi Throne Room on table, deploy on table.  Your total Force generation is +1.  Once per game, may use 3 Force to take an Effect that has no deploy cost and deploys on another card into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  May place this Effect out of play to retrieve 1 Force. (Immune to Alter.)
front.lore: Every Ewok is taught to be protective of the younger members of their clan.

conceptBy: (Original concept by Eric Hunter - Gen Con Winner 2002)
pulls: An effect that has no deploy cost and deploys on another card
pulledBy: We Wish To Board At Once
